        {
          "id": "icse_9_ch07_C_004",
          "text": "If \\(a^{\\frac{m}{n}} = b\\) where \\(a,b > 0\\), express \\(a^{\\frac{-m}{n}} + a^{\\frac{m}{n}}\\) in terms of \\(b\\).",
